fulltitle: Warren Vache on Equipment Lessons for the Horn
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Warren Vache is a supremely accomplished, versatile and rare performer. He has been astounding audiences worldwide for decades with his superb cornet, trumpet and flugelhorn stylings. In this segment, Warren compares and contrasts the cornet, the trumpet, and the flugelhorn.
